HOROSCOPE SLOTS — SIMPLE SETUP GUIDE
© SNFB by Grace 2026-2027

1. Create a GitHub account
2. Create a New Repository → name: horoscope-slots
3. Upload ALL files from the ZIP
4. Go to Settings → Pages
5. Enable GitHub Pages
6. Your live app link appears

OPTIONAL FIREBASE:
1. Go to firebase.google.com
2. Create project → Web App
3. Enable Authentication → Anonymous
4. Copy Firebase Config → paste into firebase-config.js

TESTING:
Open your GitHub Pages link on:
- iPhone
- Android
- Laptop
- Tablet

OFFLINE READY:
Your service-worker.js handles offline mode.

GOOGLE PLAY SUBMISSION:
1. Go to PWABuilder.com
2. Enter your GitHub link
3. Download Android AAB
4. Upload to Google Play Console

APPLE APP STORE:
1. PWABuilder → iOS Package
2. Upload using Xcode

YouTube:
Use promo.html to record promo video
Upload to YouTube
Replace videoId in app.js

EDITING:
You can edit:
- Names
- Icons
- Colors
- Text
- Copyright
Anytime, directly on GitHub.
